
Note:  That this will require branching the run.  Here are the steps you will need to do to continue through 2100:  


1)  cp -pR CASEROOT  CASEROOT_original
2)  Edit user_nl_cam with the new forcing files (adding your local path to inputdata)
3)  ./xmlchange RUN_TYPE=branch
4)  ./xmlchange RUN_STARTDATE=2100-01-01
5)  ./xmlchange RUN_REFCASE=original-casename
6)  ./xmlchange RUN_REFDATE=2100-01-01
7)  ./xmlchange BRNCH_RETAIN_CASENAME=TRUE
8)  ./xmlchange CONTINUE_RUN=FALSE

Here are the files you will need.  Add these files to user_nl_cam


